OL,3,CHow will a future government solve the
OL,4,Cmaternity crisis?
OL,6,FThere are almost 2,000 families in
OL,7,FNottingham who are, to date, part of
OL,8,Fthe biggest maternity investigation
OL,9,Fthe NHS has known in its history. Each
OL,10,Fone, affected by failings in care.
OL,12,FAn independent review into that care,
OL,13,Fat Nottingham University Hospitals, is
OL,14,Fexpected to be published later in
OL,15,F2025. Whoever moves into Number 10 in
OL,16,FJuly will have to add those findings
OL,17,Fto an increasing list of maternity
OL,18,Fscandals across the country.
