OL,3,CHow will a future government solve the
OL,4,Cmaternity crisis?
OL,6,FDonna Ockenden, the former senior
OL,7,Fmidwife who is leading the independent
OL,8,Freview in Nottingham, said maternity
OL,9,Fservices must be prioritised.
OL,11,F"Maternity services have to be at the
OL,12,Fvery top of the NHS agenda, put very
OL,13,Fsimply, we all need to be born" she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe former senior midwife who came to
OL,17,Fthe city just months after finalising
OL,18,Fher review into maternity failings in
OL,19,FShropshire in 2022 said two years on,
OL,20,Fher findings are only half way towards
OL,21,Fbeing put in place.
