OL,3,CHow will a future government solve the
OL,4,Cmaternity crisis?
OL,6,FShe said: "There is very urgent action
OL,7,Fthat needs to be taken by whoever
OL,8,Fforms the next government at the
OL,9,Fbeginning of July."
OL,11,FFamilies in Nottingham and elsewhere
OL,12,Fin England, have joined forces calling
OL,13,Ffor a national public inquiry.
OL,15,FJack and Sarah Hawkins became
OL,16,Fcampaigners for safer care, after
OL,17,Ftheir baby daughter Harriet's death in
OL,18,F2016, was found to be 'almost
OL,19,Fcertainly preventable'.
