OL,3,CHow will a future government solve the
OL,4,Cmaternity crisis?
OL,6,FSarah said "We're talking about dead
OL,7,Fmums, dead babies and harmed babies
OL,8,Fand in no other walk of life would
OL,9,Fthis be okay so as families we do not
OL,10,Funderstand why it is okay in maternity
OL,11,Fand we really want the next government
OL,12,Fto push that."
OL,14,FSarah Sissons is also backing that
OL,15,Fcall. Her son Ryan, now 17, suffered
OL,16,Fbrain damage from poor care after his
OL,17,Fbirth: "Maternity has been going
OL,18,Fdownhill for a lot of years now."
