OL,6,F"You hear more and more stories of
OL,7,Fpeople, all over the country that have
OL,8,Fthe same horror stories as us, that
OL,9,Fhave been quite recent and it needs to
OL,10,Fbe taken seriously. Mothers need to be
OL,11,Fsafe and babies need to be safe."
OL,13,FFelicity Benyon's bladder was removed
OL,14,Fin error during a planned c-section in
OL,15,F2015. She said it is vital the
OL,16,Fgovernment "prioritise" previous
OL,17,Frecommendations into maternity care.
