OL,3,CHow will a future government solve the
OL,4,Cmaternity crisis?
OL,6,FFamilies who are campaigning for safe
OL,7,Fcare in Nottingham said although the
OL,8,Ffinal report isn't expected to be out
OL,9,Funtil later in 2025, they hope the
OL,10,Fnext government won't wait until then
OL,11,Fto get to work on issues.
OL,13,FIn their manifesto pledge, the
OL,14,FConservatives want to prioritise
OL,15,Fwomen's health by creating local
OL,16,Fhealth hubs and commit to bring
OL,17,Fforward a comprehensive national
OL,18,Fstrategy for maternity care.
