OL,3,CHow will a future government solve the
OL,4,Cmaternity crisis?
OL,6,FLabour said they will ensure failing
OL,7,Ftrusts are supported into rapid
OL,8,Fimprovement and plan to train
OL,9,Fthousands more midwives as part of the
OL,10,FNHS Workforce Plan.
OL,12,FThe Liberal Democrats said they are
OL,13,Fcommitted to transforming perinatal
OL,14,Fmental health support for pregnant
OL,15,Fwomen, new mums and those who have
OL,16,Fexperienced miscarriage or stillbirth.
OL,17,FAs well, as creating a 10-year
OL,18,Fretention plan to help the NHS keep
OL,19,Fmore of its staff.
